Package: netmeter
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, r-base, ghostscript
Recommends: traceroute, iputils-tracepath, iputils-ping, rsplib-tools, subnetcalc (>= 2.0.2)
Description: Network Performance Meter
 NetMeter is a network performance meter for the UDP, TCP, SCTP and
 DCCP transport protocols. It simultaneously transmits bidirectional
 flows to an endpoint and measures the resulting flow bandwidths. The
 results are written as vector and scalar files. The vector files can
 be used to create PDF plots of the results.
